  _0_2h3h4|_0_0______|__0__________|_0__________|__0_________|_0_2h3h4______]  
  *(*)  Fripp improvises on this bit, so try different things out. Mostly*  
  *triple stops. e.g.,*  
  [  __5-sl-7__5-sl-7_|___  
